{"title":"Github中自定义个人主页","slug":"Github中自定义个人主页","date":"2024-11-16T12:57:34.000Z","updated":"2024-11-18T00:43:10.754Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Github中自定义个人主页.json","excerpt":" [Figure] ​在Github中设定一个账号与同名的repository即可在该仓库的readme.md​文件中自定义展示到主页的内容。","covers":["https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/12885947/1731761417027-80f8993d-9548-4d53-94e2-0533efbe32d7.png","https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/12885947/1731664630208-26ff787b-dccc-4aed-addf-d78197ea116b.png"],"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"\\assets\\js\\Meting.min.js\"></script><div id=\"vip-container\"><h2 id=\"​\"><img data-src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/12885947/1731761417027-80f8993d-9548-4d53-94e2-0533efbe32d7.png\" alt=\"\">​</h2>\n<p>在Github中设定一个账号与同名的repository即可在该仓库的<code>readme.md</code>​文件中自定义展示到主页的内容。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p>​<img data-src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/12885947/1731664630208-26ff787b-dccc-4aed-addf-d78197ea116b.png\" alt=\"\">​</p>\n<p><strong>leafminer/leafminer</strong> is a ✨<em>special</em> ✨ repository that you can use to add a <code>README.md</code>​ to your GitHub profile. Make sure it’s public and initialize it with a <strong>README</strong> to get started.</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考\">参考</h2>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly96aHVhbmxhbi56aGlodS5jb20vcC8xODkyNDkwNTA=\">自定义你的github主页 - 知乎<i class=\"fa fa-external-link-alt\"></i></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9iYnMuaHVhd2VpY2xvdWQuY29tL2Jsb2dzLzQyMTgyNQ==\">GitHub教程-自定义个人页制作-云社区-华为云<i class=\"fa fa-external-link-alt\"></i></span></p>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<script src=\"https://my.openwrite.cn/js/readmore.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\n\t\t\t<script>\n\t\t\tvar isMobile = navigator.userAgent.match(/(phone|pad|pod|iPhone|iPod|ios|iPad|Android|Mobile|BlackBerry|IEMobile|MQQBrowser|JUC|Fennec|wOSBrowser|BrowserNG|WebOS|Symbian|Windows Phone)/i);\n\t\t\tif (!isMobile) {\n\t\t\t    var btw = new BTWPlugin();\n\t\t\t    btw.init({\n\t\t\t        \"id\": \"vip-container\",\n\t\t\t        \"blogId\": \"33502-1730425843713-524\",\n\t\t\t        \"name\": \"虫子的生存笔记\",\n\t\t\t        \"qrcode\": \"https://leaf-miner.pages.dev/image/%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%8F%B7.png\",\n\t\t\t        \"keyword\": \"more\"\n\t\t\t    });\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t</script>\n\t\t","more":"<p>​<img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/12885947/1731664630208-26ff787b-dccc-4aed-addf-d78197ea116b.png\" alt=\"\">​</p>\n<p><strong>leafminer/leafminer</strong> is a ✨<em>special</em> ✨ repository that you can use to add a <code>README.md</code>​ to your GitHub profile. Make sure it’s public and initialize it with a <strong>README</strong> to get started.</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考\">参考</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/189249050\">自定义你的github主页 - 知乎</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bbs.huaweicloud.com/blogs/421825\">GitHub教程-自定义个人页制作-云社区-华为云</a></p>","categories":[{"name":"笔记","path":"api/categories/笔记.json"},{"name":"其他","path":"api/categories/其他.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"主页展示","path":"api/tags/主页展示.json"},{"name":"Github","path":"api/tags/Github.json"},{"name":"个人主页","path":"api/tags/个人主页.json"}]}